info.description:
This microservice deals with all the operations and functionalities that a professional user needs, ranging from performing a login to get access to the application to changing his/her password.The detailed operations are:
 -Login
 -First login / password change. This includes the voluntary password change as well as the forgotten password change and the password reset.
 -Professional offered services 
 URL Confluence : https://steps.everis.com/confluence/display/PROLEMER/Endpoint+Login+Professional

username.description:
This atribute contains de emails user 
 Must match the regular expression [A-Za-z0-9]+(?:[\.\-\_]?[A-Za-z0-9]+)+@[A-Za-z0-9]+(?:[\.\-\_][A-Za-z0-9]+)*(?:[\.][A-Za-z0-9]+)+ when mandatory or filled.

password.description:
This atribute contains de password 
 Encoded in base 64
